		nīr <unclear>vi</unclear> li Uḷiṭṭu Eppēṟpaṭṭa Iṟaiyum
		<lb n="2"/>koḷḷa p<choice><sic>i</sic><corr>e</corr></choice>ṟātōm ākavum
	</p>
	<p>
		piṭāri-kōyilukku teṟkku
		Oru ko <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> kati-k-karaiyum avikkuṇtilukku mēṟkkum
		Ivv-uṇ-ṇilam oḻiv' iṉṟi aṉupōcippār ākavum
	</p>
	<p>  	
		<lb n="3"/> Iv-vūr ma<choice><orig>ṇṇ</orig><reg>ṇ</reg></choice>utaiyarkaḷum piṭāri-kōyilukku pukum vaḻiyē pukku kāṭukāl kōṭṭam ārāticcu pōka-p peṟuvarkaḷ ākavum
	</p>
	<p>
		Ip-paric' oṭṭi kututtōm <hi rend="grantha">sabhai</hi>yōm
	</p>
	<p>
		<lb n="4"/>rakṣittār aṭi y-eṉ talai mēḻiṉa
